> >> >> >>>>> things like
> >> >> >>>>>
> >> >> >>>>>   unwanted_foo_symbols <- ... long and complicated expression
> >> >> >>>>>                               eventually calling user-defined
> >> >> >>>>> helper
> >> >> >>>>>                               functions located in the
