Subject: [Bioc-devel] Updating package NEWS files for Bioconductor 3.3
 release announcement (and biocViews)
In-Reply-To: <9224_1444256122_5615997A_9224_13619_1_1109023958.200084.1444256097427.JavaMail.root@fredhutch.org>
